Ideabox

This is a basic project to create, edit, delete, sort, and like ideas.
It was created as an assignment at the Turing School of Software and Design: turing.io .
The basic tutorial is found here: http://tutorials.jumpstartlab.com/projects/idea_box.html


Setup

Clone the repo. Cd into the project directory(ideabox2). Bundle to ensure all dependencies are installed.
Run from the command line using rackup.


